鑑定是否是一仔 細佬想問一般要等幾耐 同埋會點罰 因為係第一次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩龜<br />\n金錢既話就pk</blockquote><br />\n輻射龜"},{"pid":"1044fb219bc20a8d88b4e67694ce9d3b82742ba6","tid":102693,"uid":31927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:33:04.000Z","msg":"輻射龜，屬於陸龜科，瀕臨絕種的爬蟲類之一。<br />\n仆街啦你"},{"pid":"0ddb334cfc1b2ab1239e90ebfc445a94abe64f2d","tid":102693,"uid":31927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:33:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輻射龜，屬於陸龜科，瀕臨絕種的爬蟲類之一。<br />\n仆街啦你</blockquote><br />\n射紋龜被瀕危野生動植物種國際貿易公約列於附錄一，則禁止捕捉任何野生的龜隻，亦禁止其非法買賣。而射紋龜的原生地馬達加斯加亦有人工繁殖的保育工作正在進行，以提升此龜種的數量。"},{"pid":"72edd29520f3f85845c6217fbd2b2d69e6695655","tid":102693,"uid":56441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:34:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輻射龜，屬於陸龜科，瀕臨絕種的爬蟲類之一。<br />\n仆街啦你</blockquote><br />\n知唔知會點判"},{"pid":"1499cbbc3924a14a12fd2132584305495d9b9665","tid":102693,"uid":40499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:35:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>輻射龜，屬於陸龜科，瀕臨絕種的爬蟲類之一。<br />\n仆街啦你</blockquote><br />\n知唔知會點判</blockquote><br />\n無事既 你有無錢？"},{"pid":"58c5fe042b78ac79c6ca2ede1b996c4828ebc635","tid":102693,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a655a3b995af26f97b0705af0137d6a8f7cea1","tid":102693,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:35:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>是咁的，細佬我12/10/2016比漁記放蛇 扮買家約出來 充公左隻龜 佢話要等專家鑑定是否是一仔 細佬想問一般要等幾耐 同埋會點罰 因為係第一次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩龜<br />\n金錢既話就pk</blockquote><br />\n輻射龜</blockquote><br />\n輻射都係一級<br />\n如果唔係一仔⋯你真係大檸樂"},{"pid":"9eba2b5a37b968f4aebc84bea384ea684730c463","tid":102693,"uid":32527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗定屎忽"},{"pid":"a4b548b636667d09757bc61ac1051fa52cf32742","tid":102693,"uid":1667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:39:45.000Z","msg":"Fb放蛇？"},{"pid":"fd11332042e6875571d4de6e5c73de1a697b665c","tid":102693,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:39:46.000Z","msg":"(1) 除第47條另有規定外，除非&mdash;<br />\n(a) 符合第17或22條的規定；或<br />\n(b) 附錄I物種的標本是根據和按照下述文件而進口的&mdash;<br />\n(i) 事先根據第23(1)(a)條就該標本發出的許可證；及<br />\n(ii) 就該標本發出的《公約》證明文件，<br />\n否則任何人不得進口附錄I物種的標本。<br />\n(2) 根據和按照第(1)(b)(i)及(ii)款提述的文件進口附錄I物種的標本的人，須在該標本進入<br />\n香港境內時&mdash;<br />\n(a) 向獲授權人員出示或安排向獲授權人員出示有關的許可證；及<br />\n(b) 向獲授權人員交出或安排向獲授權人員交出有關的《公約》證明文件，以供保留及取<br />\n消。<br />\n(3) 任何人違反第(1)或(2)款，即屬犯罪，一經定罪，可處第6級罰款及監禁1年。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.legislation.gov.hk/blis_pdf.nsf/6799165D2FEE3FA94825755E0033E532/4E3EEBAB4FA9956E482575EF001F5657/$FILE/CAP_586_c_b5.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legislation.gov.hk%2Fblis_pdf.nsf%2F6799165D2FEE3FA94825755E0033E532%2F4E3EEBAB4FA9956E482575EF001F5657%2F%24FILE%2FCAP_586_c_b5.pdf&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a24984c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.legislation.gov.hk/blis_pdf.nsf/6799165D2FEE3FA94825755E0033E532/4E3EEBAB4FA9956E482575EF001F5657/$FILE/CAP_586_c_b5.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n樓主大獲了"},{"pid":"83e4dc615906e861c020238dc2b752e3a16c38f1","tid":102693,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:41:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>(1) 除第47條另有規定外，除非&mdash;<br />\n(a) 符合第17或22條的規定；或<br />\n(b) 附錄I物種的標本是根據和按照下述文件而進口的&mdash;<br />\n(i) 事先根據第23(1)(a)條就該標本發出的許可證；及<br />\n(ii) 就該標本發出的《公約》證明文件，<br />\n否則任何人不得進口附錄I物種的標本。<br />\n(2) 根據和按照第(1)(b)(i)及(ii)款提述的文件進口附錄I物種的標本的人，須在該標本進入<br />\n香港境內時&mdash;<br />\n(a) 向獲授權人員出示或安排向獲授權人員出示有關的許可證；及<br />\n(b) 向獲授權人員交出或安排向獲授權人員交出有關的《公約》證明文件，以供保留及取<br />\n消。<br />\n(3) 任何人違反第(1)或(2)款，即屬犯罪，一經定罪，可處第6級罰款及監禁1年。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.legislation.gov.hk/blis_pdf.nsf/6799165D2FEE3FA94825755E0033E532/4E3EEBAB4FA9956E482575EF001F5657/$FILE/CAP_586_c_b5.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legislation.gov.hk%2Fblis_pdf.nsf%2F6799165D2FEE3FA94825755E0033E532%2F4E3EEBAB4FA9956E482575EF001F5657%2F%24FILE%2FCAP_586_c_b5.pdf&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a24984c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.legislation.gov.hk/blis_pdf.nsf/6799165D2FEE3FA94825755E0033E532/4E3EEBAB4FA9956E482575EF001F5657/$FILE/CAP_586_c_b5.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n樓主大獲了</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個係標本"},{"pid":"f33729b5c9d4600eaaea9b89cd164e869bd9b0a8","tid":102693,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:41:06.000Z","msg":"私人轉讓而無合法許可証<br />\n要10萬、監禁一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n商業就最高500萬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我諗你十萬八萬走唔甩"},{"pid":"78a5ea772c09a81043fe65702e065ed077f61378","tid":102693,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19def7dd1853a9560896526c111a1538c8b84eb6","tid":102693,"uid":56441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:42:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>私人轉讓而無合法許可証<br />\n要10萬、監禁一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n商業就最高500萬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我諗你十萬八萬走唔甩</blockquote><br />\n咁大獲"},{"pid":"e7c18282a75edb6076eb4d10d49d9f6e0f28785d","tid":102693,"uid":56441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:42:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Fb放蛇？</blockquote><br />\n是的師兄"},{"pid":"02230ddb7a89fe7c695b4d327fa44583a5375a0b","tid":102693,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:43:04.000Z","msg":"條： 9 對管有或控制附錄I物種的標本的限制 L.N. 206 of 2006 01/12/2006<br />\n(1) 除第47條另有規定外，除非&mdash;<br />\n(a) 符合第20或22條的規定；或<br />\n(b) 附錄I物種的標本是根據和按照根據第23(1)(e)條就該標本發出的許可證而被管有或控<br />\n制的，<br />\n否則任何人不得管有或控制附錄I物種的標本。<br />\n(2) 任何人違反第(1)款，即屬犯罪，一經定罪，可處第6級罰款及監禁1年。<br />\n條： 10 為商業目的而犯關於附錄I物種的標本的罪行的較重懲罰 L.N. 206 of 2006 01/12/2006<br />\n如任何人就某作為(包括管有或控制標本)而被裁定犯第5、6、7、8或9條所訂罪行，而法庭信納<br />\n該作為是為商業目的而作出(不論是由該人作出或由他人代該人作出)的，則該人可被處罰款<br />\n$5000000及監禁2年，以代替該等條文訂明的懲罰。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.legislation.gov.hk/blis_pdf.nsf/6799165D2FEE3FA94825755E0033E532/4E3EEBAB4FA9956E482575EF001F5657/$FILE/CAP_586_c_b5.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legislation.gov.hk%2Fblis_pdf.nsf%2F6799165D2FEE3FA94825755E0033E532%2F4E3EEBAB4FA9956E482575EF001F5657%2F%24FILE%2FCAP_586_c_b5.pdf&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a24984c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.legislation.gov.hk/blis_pdf.nsf/6799165D2FEE3FA94825755E0033E532/4E3EEBAB4FA9956E482575EF001F5657/$FILE/CAP_586_c_b5.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa57567c77b18957364d69748c69e57b86cde3f7","tid":102693,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:43:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Fb放蛇？</blockquote><br />\n是的師兄</blockquote><br />\n開下年先啦"},{"pid":"4eb853d097dc98170b5c2cca7d65f899704c6c4b","tid":102693,"uid":56441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:43:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Fb放蛇？</blockquote